title: Deribit Integration Crashes Octobot
body:
: Describe your environment
  * OS : UBUNTU
  * Python Version: 3.7
 
When I add Deribit and leave the api credentials on default or customized Octobot fails to start and crashes.
A clear and concise description of what the bug is.
Logs:
2019-07-02 13:38:37,186 ERROR    OctoBot Launcher     OctoBot Exception : argument of type 'NoneType' is not iterable
